Interface.SqlSentence: select view_hh_pacsjk.DJLSH PATIENTID, view_hh_pacsjk.DJLSH HIS_ID, view_hh_pacsjk.XM PatName, '' IDCard, '' PatType, case view_hh_pacsjk.XB when '1' then 'M' when '0' then 'F' when '%' then 'O' else view_hh_pacsjk.XB end PatSex, view_hh_pacsjk.CSNYR PatBirthday, view_hh_pacsjk.NL PatAge, '' Address, '' TelephoneNo, '' OrderType, view_hh_pacsjk.TJXMBH ExamItemID, view_hh_pacsjk.MC ExamItem, '' ExamDr, '' OrderDrID, '' OrderDr, '' OrderDT, '' OutpatientID, view_hh_pacsjk.MT Modality, '' Disease, '' PostCode, '' Occupation, '' Country, '' Nationality, '' ClinicID, '' Clinic, '' InpatientID, '' Charge, view_hh_pacsjk.TJLX , view_hh_pacsjk.DJLSH PhysicalExamID from view_hh_pacsjk where view_hh_pacsjk.DJLSH = '{0}' and view_hh_pacsjk.MT = '{1}' and view_hh_pacsjk.TJLX = '1001'
